ak at det ligger mindre ordrereserver i avtalen n\u00e5 enn vi hadde i juli i fjor. Da synes vi det ogs\u00e5 er fornuftig at prisen gjenspeiler dette, uttalte kommunikasjonsdirekt\u00f8r \u00d8yvind Risnes i Bergen Group da."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e59df2ad43acaa2dd4ca6c27929626c1551d343c20a0f14704210c6d39d146a8"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-09-25T20:28:21.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Bergen Group har solgt seg helt ut av verftet i Rissa."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article10031421.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/FOSEN%20MEK%20UKRAINA.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/03e4ec2f73923c4ff0985313ead74549909feae3.jpg?598887f1"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Rissa-verft p\u00e5 utenlandske hender -adressa.no", "- Tidligere enn planlagt", "Store tap", "Lavere pris"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "03e4ec2f73923c4ff0985313ead74549909feae3"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "personal-finance"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["noryards as", "bergen group"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["eid", "prosent", "aksjer", "ukrainske selskapet", "pris", "utenlandske hender", "lavere pris", "verftet", "millioner kroner"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["group og calexco", "noryards", "calexco", "fosen mek"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "rissa"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["as